Define __DF_PROP_MARK for $10000000
Define __DF_PROP_SET_BIT for (__DF_PROP_MARK ior $20000000)

Class cWebBaseObject is a cObject
End_Class

Define _SetWebProp_Addr for (!a + 2)
Procedure Set SetWebProp for cWebBaseObject Variant vValue
    Handle hmSetter
    
    Move (CURRENT_MESSAGE ior __DF_PROP_SET_BIT) to hmSetter
    
    Send MarkWebPropChanged CURRENT_MESSAGE
    
    //  Forward to actual property set
    Forward Set hmSetter to vValue
End_Procedure